sections.content_markdown:
Override container alignment for specific items using `justify-self`, `align-self`, and `place-self`.

:::code[language="css" title="Self Alignment Properties"]
.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 150px);
  place-items: center; /* Default for all items */
}

.special-item {
  /* Override for this item only */
  justify-self: end;
  align-self: start;

  /* Or use shorthand */
  place-self: start end; /* align / justify */
}
:::

:::code[language="html" title="Mixed Alignment Example"]
<style>
.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  grid-template-rows: repeat(2, 100px);
  gap: 10px;
  place-items: center; /* Default centering */
}

.item-1 { place-self: start; }      /* Top-left */
.item-2 { /* Uses default center */ }
.item-3 { place-self: start end; }  /* Top-right */
.item-4 { place-self: end start; }  /* Bottom-left */
.item-5 { place-self: stretch; }    /* Fill cell */
.item-6 { place-self: end; }        /* Bottom-right */
</style>

<div class="grid">
  <div class="item item-1">1</div>
  <div class="item item-2">2</div>
  <div class="item item-3">3</div>
  <div class="item item-4">4</div>
  <div class="item item-5">5</div>
  <div class="item item-6">6</div>
</div>
:::

:::steps[title="Creating Asymmetric Layouts"]
## Step 1: Set default alignment
```css
.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;
  place-items: start;
}
```

## Step 2: Override specific items
```css
.hero-image {
  place-self: center;
}

.sidebar {
  align-self: stretch;
}

.call-to-action {
  place-self: end center;
}
```
:::

:::realworld[title="Dashboard Card Layout"]
```html
<div class="dashboard-grid">
  <div class="stat-card">Revenue</div>
  <div class="stat-card">Users</div>
  <div class="chart-card">Big Chart</div>
  <div class="list-card">Recent Activity</div>
</div>

<style>
.dashboard-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  place-items: stretch; /* Cards fill their cells */
}

.chart-card {
  grid-column: span 2;
  grid-row: span 2;
}

.list-card {
  grid-column: span 2;
  align-self: start; /* Don't stretch vertically */
}
</style>
```
:::

